{"tid":1502473,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【825荃葵】提下大家，我地天橋戰未贏過，唔好輕敵","createTime":"2019-08-24T16:27:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T04:40:51.000Z","uid":114801,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d72aaea3b4176761cc6054aaf527435078dbd529","tid":1502473,"uid":114801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:27:51.000Z","msg":"歷史回顧：<br />\n上環-比狗搶左條橋高空任射<br />\n上水-有手足比狗追到推埋落橋<br />\n沙田-希爾頓果幾兄弟連接位完全失守<br />\n今晚黃大仙-速狗兩邊跑上橋，圍左一堆街坊<br />\n<br />\n8.5荃灣完全唔可以作參考用，因為遍地開花，完全無狗理，係後尾d示威者去圍新界南總對家先勉強湊隊狗出黎放tg。<br />\n<br />\n地形重點：<br />\n<br />\n重點一、荃灣天橋好撚重要，一旦比狗清左天橋：<br />\nA. 所有rb如同虛設，逃生路線非常危險，狗狗可以一路睇住你走一路進行圍捕<br />\nB. <span style=\"color: red;\">天橋範圍太廣太長，記者影唔曬，高空開槍都無人知</span>（上環起碼有記者影到）<br />\nC. 封左橋同封左荃灣地鐵站無分別<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重點二、眾安街二坡坊果頭算係荃灣無天橋既地方，不過有黑社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重點三、荃灣仲有個西鐵站，不過因為近海皮，如果狗鐵封左荃灣西，地形極不利<br />\n<br />\n重點四、荃灣有兩個狗屋，一個響愉景，一個大窩口（新界南總），危險勿近。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論：<br />\n<br />\n個人建議拿拿林行完就搭車去春袋算<br />\n<br />\n以上純粹個人見解，僅供參考"},{"pid":"8b8e8dba2665675c03e2f081e5ccebf6615f25c2","tid":1502473,"uid":114801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:32:06.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"7c7098d715a5087aaa071928615eb79ebf8861d4","tid":1502473,"uid":182061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:33:09.000Z","msg":"街坊守天橋"},{"pid":"c3852adfe4e7f9a35d7e2bb6b47245601c227009","tid":1502473,"uid":53415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:34:27.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n唔好只睇路戰<br />\n要睇埋天橋戰<br />\n佔高點"},{"pid":"0ed43992270c01dc76b0e4dc0550019da40149f0","tid":1502473,"uid":101498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:37:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vEhtr7b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvEhtr7b.png&h=d0ab0272&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">光復香港，時代革命</div></span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db01874a11b1e3a71602897023554cfe775cdd24","tid":1502473,"uid":114801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3852adfe4e7f9a35d7e2bb6b47245601c227009","tid":1502473,"uid":53415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:34:27.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n唔好只睇路戰<br />\n要睇埋天橋戰<br />\n佔高點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:38:47.000Z","msg":"武力、資訊、組織力完全唔對等<br />\n<br />\n天橋戰未贏過<br />\n<br />\n無論你有幾多萬人，響天橋口，得5-6個可以企最前"},{"pid":"0e3e2cef6f3fd3ba5346140760eb32aec3239b8d","tid":1502473,"uid":284696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:40:45.000Z","msg":"去春袋"},{"pid":"24f3331dc0c2720c629203e9efccba5c69eee43e","tid":1502473,"uid":53415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db01874a11b1e3a71602897023554cfe775cdd24","tid":1502473,"uid":114801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3852adfe4e7f9a35d7e2bb6b47245601c227009","tid":1502473,"uid":53415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:34:27.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n唔好只睇路戰<br />\n要睇埋天橋戰<br />\n佔高點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16: